Meanwhile, AAP candidate Rajesh Nama Bansiwala exuded confidence that the party would win all the 70 seats this time. â€œFor the past five years, the MLA has not been seen here and no development work has been done. Vijender Gupta has not even pruned the trees here. For the past 25 years, the BJP MLA has looted the people of Rohini,â€ Bansiwala told indianexpress.com.

